      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] to me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then start over [? close, ?] and [? close. ?] And we come-- and I see my mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
